OWAYENGUMSAKAZI woKhozi FM, uNgizwe Mchunu, wake wathi "Uhlanya olugqoka uthayi alulapheki." Ngangithi useqalwa ukugula kodwa sengiyabona ukuthi wayeqinisile. UMalesela Teffo ungomunye walabo bantu ababeshiwo nguNgizwe. Angazi sekukangaki ebanga isicefe eNkantolo eNkulu yasePretoria ngisho engasamele muntu. Okubuhlungu lesi sidina asibangayo siphazamisa ukuqulwa kwecala lokubulawa kukaSenzo Meyiwa. Abamjwayele abasivimbele yena ngoba usenesicefe.